:: Hero {"position":"1175,1275","size":"100,100"}
"Very well," says the LemonHead. "I will give you a magical talisman that will protect you from the dragon's flames. Good luck on your journey young one!"
You make your way to the caves and confront the dragon. With the help of the talisman, you are able to defeat the dragon and claim the Enchanted Sword. You return to the kingdom as a hero, and peace is restored at last.



:: Journey Start {"position":"2425,775","size":"100,100"}
The Quest for the Enchanted Sword

You are a brave knight, tasked with finding the legendary Enchanted weapon that contains contains paracausal  power to bring peace to the kingdom. The kingdom has been in chaos since the death of the King.  Whoever wields the Enchanted weapon will be recognized as the rightful ruler of the kingdom. 


[[Embark->Village Square]]


:: Mountains {"position":"1750,1250","size":"100,100"}
--Mountains--

The mountains are treacherous, but you make your way to the Lemonhead's cave. The hermit greets you warmly and offers you a cup of green herb. 
"I've heard of the Enchanted Weapon," he says. "It's said to be guarded by a powerful tribe of centaurs in the caves beyond the mountains. However, there is a catch. The centaurs will only surrender the weapon to a strong hero that will be facing theri strongest warrior. Do you have what it takes? Unless... There is one other way but it is  a more dangerous and bloody way. 

[[I'll do anything for this crown!!!!->Corruption]]
[[I am a true hero->Hero]]







