:: Tavern {"position":"1900,1025","size":"100,100"}
The tavern is full of patrons, drinking and laughing. You approach the barkeep and ask him about the Enchanted weapon.
"Ah, the Enchanted weapon!" he exclaims. "I've heard tales of it, but I don't know where it is. However, I can offer you some advice. You should seek out the wise LemonHead who lives in the mountains. He might know something."


[[Go to the mountains->Mountains]]
